      "id": 104,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Orders by status — NOT YET EMITTED",
      "description": "Placeholder for the brief's orders-by-status (stacked) panel.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "restaurant-prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 37 },
      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**No `orders_by_status` gauge exists in the implemented P7-T10 metric set.** The Phase 7 Task 10 plan defines only: `http_requests_total`, `http_request_duration_seconds`, `outbox_deliveries_total`, `sla_breaches_total`, `rate_limit_rejections_total`. When an order-status gauge is added (suggested: `orders_by_status{restaurant_id,status}` registered on `app.obs.metrics.REGISTRY`, updated by a beat task), replace this panel with a stacked timeseries of `sum by (status) (orders_by_status)`. SLA breaches (above) are the only order-level signal available today."
      }
    }
